text.title: BINNENGEKOMEN.
text.p: TEXEL, 30 April; Flinn, Thomson, Seaham. - Belt, Freeman, Sunderland. - Christiania, Harris, Christiania. - Olaf Kyrre, Christcnsen, Drammen. — 1 Mei; Edith Maria, Hall, Newc. - Emil, Richelsen, Frederikstad. - Odin, Torkelsen, id. - Gesina, Riks, Oudsoen. (Benevens de schepen per telegram gemeld). VLIE, 30 April; Ettje, Haak, Odensee. - Amsterdam, S., Hamburg. HELLEVOETSLUIS, 30 April; Jabez, Lucas, Newc. - Bctty & Jane, Todd, id. - Harmony, Rilwood, id. - Statesman, Bolton, Middlesbro. - Colletis, S., Goole. - Randers, Sörensen, Randers. - Thoerkelsen Minde, Christiansen, Horscns. - Cornet, Pedersen, Landscrona.— 1 Mei; Earl of Auckland, S., Londen. - Theresc, S., Grangemouth. - Vinsage, Osborne, Newc. - Forest Queen, S., Hartlepool. - Emanuel, Bjerkeness, Holmstrand. BRIELLE, 1 Mei; de Maas, S., Londen. - Batavier, S., id. - Norfolk, S., Goöle.
ANTWERPEN, 1 MeijHertha, Warnaar, Buenos-Ayres. GENUA, 26 April; Bérénice, S., Livorno.
LISSABON, 23 April; Geertruida Jacoba, Pottjer, Triest. PARA, 7 Maart; Terschelling, Rotgans, Antw. NEW-YORK, 19 April; in lading: Henny, Ohlerich, Amst.- Herzoe Paul, Groth,Rott. s
